Part 3: Question 6 Section 1

sas2$target1<-case_when(
  sas2$age<40~"young",
  TRUE ~"old"
)
sas_predict2<-sas2 %>% select("sex","raceethn","provider","moa","mod","admtype","campus","los","target1")

sas_predict3<-sas_predict2 %>% filter(raceethn!="",admtype!="")

set.seed(2020)
splitIndex1<-createDataPartition(sas_predict3$target1,p=.05,list=FALSE)

df_train1<-sas_predict3[splitIndex1,]
df_test1<-sas_predict3[-splitIndex1,]
